OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773331877
OL,3,CTwo charged after man 'with most
OL,4,Ccaring soul' killed in crash
OL,6,FTwo men have been charged after a 50-
OL,7,Fyear-old man was killed in a crash.
OL,9,FThe charges follow a collision
OL,10,Finvolving two cars on Kingsway, at the
OL,11,Fjunction with Green End Road, in south
OL,12,FManchester in the early hours of
OL,13,FMonday, 9 March 2026.
OL,15,FSylvester Abayomi, known
OL,16,Faffectionately as "Syll", was driving
OL,17,Fa Volvo S40 when it collided with a
OL,18,FVolkswagen Golf at approximately
OL,19,F4:30am.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
