PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773331877
OL,3,CTwo charged after man 'with most
OL,4,Ccaring soul' killed in crash
OL,6,FHe suffered serious injuries and later
OL,7,Fdied in hospital, Greater Manchester
OL,8,FPolice said.
OL,10,FSyll's partner, Denise, described him
OL,11,Fas "the most caring soul" and a
OL,12,F"gentle person" who would be missed by
OL,13,Feveryone.
OL,15,FTwo men have now been charged
OL,16,Ffollowing an investigation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
