PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773331877
OL,3,CTwo charged after man 'with most
OL,4,Ccaring soul' killed in crash
OL,6,FUways Hussain, of Burnage, Manchester,
OL,7,Fis charged with causing death by
OL,8,Fdangerous driving; causing death by
OL,9,Fdriving a vehicle whilst uninsured and
OL,10,Fconspiracy to pervert the course of
OL,11,Fjustice.
OL,13,FThe 20-year-old is also charged with
OL,14,Ffailing to provide a specimen for
OL,15,Fanalysis and driving without insurance.
OL,17,FUsmon Mahmood, 23, of Levenshulme, is
OL,18,Fcharged with aiding and abetting
OL,19,Fcausing death by dangerous driving and
OL,20,Faiding and abetting causing death by
OL,21,Fdriving a vehicle whilst uninsured.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773331877
OL,3,CTwo charged after man 'with most
OL,4,Ccaring soul' killed in crash
OL,6,FThe 23-year-old is also charged with
OL,7,Fconspiracy to pervert the course of
OL,8,Fjustice.
OL,10,FBoth Hussain and Mahmood were remanded
OL,11,Fin police custody and were due to
OL,12,Fappear at Stockport Magistrates' Court
OL,13,Fon Thursday, 12 March 2026.
OL,15,FPolice are continuing to appeal for
OL,16,Fanyone with dashcam or CCTV footage of
OL,17,Fthe incident to contact the Serious
OL,18,FCollision Investigation Unit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
